    "content": "---\ndesc: <span>Buttons</span> express what action will occur when the user clicks or touches it. Buttons are used to initialize an action, either in the background or foreground of an experience.\nvariations:\n  primary-button:\n  - Primary button\n  secondary-button:\n  - Secondary button\n  ghost-button:\n  - Ghost button\n---\n"
